/// CityManager — demo row-level security role. Members see only sites whose city matches their
/// mapping. The filter below is a demo placeholder (city = USERPRINCIPALNAME()); replace with a
/// security-mapping table in production. Object-level security hiding customer email/phone for this
/// role is applied by fabric/scripts/30_create_semantic_model.py via TOM set_ols (R2).
role CityManager
	modelPermission: read

	tablePermission dim_site = 'dim_site'[city] = USERPRINCIPALNAME()

	annotation Zava_RLS_Note = Demo RLS; map members to a city via a security table in production.
